These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, card-games, fishing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, action, family, drama
City: venice, hamburg, marseilles, paris
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, frog, rabbit
1. the person watching action movies is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
7. the person watching action movies is the owner of the cat##1
8. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
9. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | board-games  | fishing  | camping | card-games |
| Movie-Genre           | action | animation | drama  | family  |
| City   | paris       | marseilles      | venice | hamburg      |
| Pet           | cat          | fish     | frog    | rabbit     |

