.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, sprite, tea
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, kiwi, orange, papaya
City: miami, colone, marseilles, prague
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, daffodil, amaryllis, aconite
1. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to prague is the person who growszinnia##1
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
5. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person traveling to marseilles##1
7. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
9. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | cola       | iced-tea | tea        |
| Food          | papaya     | kiwi       | orange   | broccoli   |
| City   | marseilles      | colone       | prague     | miami    |
| Flower         | amaryllis | aconite | zinnia | daffodil |

