.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, november, may, august
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, electrician, librarian, security-guard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, musical, scientific
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, van, trike, subway
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is the person driving the subway##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the electrician##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the designer##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Birthday      | november | april       | august        | may        |
| Job           | electrician   | librarian | designer   | security-guard |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | horror    | scientific | musical        |
| Transport           | trike         | snowmobile  | subway       | van         |

