.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, firefighter, scientist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, electronic, funk
4 different games are played: chess, canasta, bridge, whist
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, peach, cherry, radish
1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the bartender##1
2. the firefighter is on the right of the person eating radish##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
4. the scientist is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
6. the fan of funk is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the scientist is on the right of the bartender##1
8. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
9. the person eating cherry is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Job           | engineer   | bartender  | scientist | firefighter |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | funk       | d&b       | ambient     |
| Game   | bridge       | whist    | canasta     | chess  |
| Food           | peach     | cherry | radish     | lettuce         |

