2. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
6. the person who likes azure is the person traveling to hamburg##1
7. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
8. the social-worker is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
9. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Job           | analyst  | teacher    | social-worker | videographer |
| Movie-Genre   | spy      | romance    | drama         | superhero    |
| City   | liverpool   | hannover     | hamburg          | san-francisco      |
| Color         | ebony | ivory | azure      | black      |

