.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, blueberry, orange, pomegranate
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, photography, baking, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, climbing, basketball, water-polo
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, horse, mouse
 1. the person eating orange is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 2. the person eating banana is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 4. the owner of the horse is the person eating banana##1
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 6. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | banana  | pomegranate | orange     | blueberry |
| Hobby           | baking  | woodworking      | singing | photography    |
| Sport   | climbing | basketball  | skiing    | water-polo  |
| Pet           | horse   | mouse       | fish       | frog      |

