.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
City: hannover, new-york, liverpool, prague
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, sudoku, woodworking
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, bluemaster, dannemann, dunhill
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, scooter, taxi
 1. the chaman-smoker is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the chaman-smoker is the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left##1
 9. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| City    | hannover | new-york     | liverpool    | prague |
| Hobby       | baking | sudoku    | woodworking | cooking |
| Cigar         | bluemaster   | dannemann  | dunhill        | chaman    |
| Transport   | taxi   | quad-bike | airplane    | scooter |

