3. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
4. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the fan of funk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the fan of folk is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
7. the person who likes lavender is the person driving the bus##1
8. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking 7up##1
9. the person driving the skateboard is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage      | water      | 7up         | milk        | juice      |
| Color           | lavender | purple | black  | blue  |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | folk     | salsa | soul     |
| Transport     | bus        | scooter     | jet-ski     | skateboard |

