 7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3       |     4     |
| Sport          | badminton  | volleyball   | golf       | skiing     |
